notes.text: This advisory aggregates security fixes for the java-11-openjdk SRPM in CIQ LTS for Rocky Linux 8.8. It addresses 16 CVEs: CVE-2023-48161, CVE-2024-21011, CVE-2024-21012, CVE-2024-21068, CVE-2024-21085, and 11 more.
